-- Other nations have faith U.S. will back IMF reforms -official
-- By Anna Yukhananov and Krista Hughes
-- Fri Apr 11, 2014 02:02PM EDT
-- None



WASHINGTON, April 11 (Reuters) - IMF member nations trust the United States will eventually back reforms to give emerging economies more power at the global lender, the chair of the International Monetary Fund's steering committee said on Friday.

